周日及法定节假日8:30-18:00。', 6375, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://travel.qunar.com/p-oi705067-bazhaigou', '', '2', '4', '5', '2', '1', 5, 46738, 144, NULL, 48883, 80090, 336253, 34938, 10039, 6427, '2011-08-04 00:00:00', '2011-08-05 00:00:00', NULL);
