-83804412', 'http://www.xzmuseum.com/', '（周二-周日）9:00-17:00（16:30停止领票入馆），周一闭馆。', 1207, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2小时', 'http://travel.qunar.com/p-oi706232-xuzhoubowuguan', '5', '', '2', '', '3', '5', 3, 44255, 195, 285055, NULL, 42234, NULL, 21061, 236767, 93792, '2011-08-04 00:00:00', '2011-08-05 00:00:00', NULL);
